    Previously, I worked at <em>Company X</em> as a product designer, and at <em
      >Company Y</em
    > where I helped build their design system.
  </p>

  <h2>Writing</h2>
  <div class="writing-list">
    <a href="/post-1" class="writing-item">
      <span class="writing-title">Title of the first post</span>
      <span class="writing-date no-underline">2024</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/post-2" class="writing-item">
      <span class="writing-title">Another interesting post</span>
      <span class="writing-date no-underline">2023</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Writing list */
  .writing-list {
    @apply space-y-3 mt-6;
  }

  .writing-item {
    @apply flex items-center justify-between py-3 -mx-3 px-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-neutral-100 transition-colors;
  }

  .writing-title {
    @apply text-neutral-900;
  }

  .writing-date {
    @apply text-neutral-500 text-sm;
  }
</style>
